              <p class="govuk-body">No, this seems new.</p>
              <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-7" id="is-this-a-common-need"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project/is-this-a-common-need#is-this-a-common-need" class="govuk-link">2. Is this a common need?</a></h2>
