              <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-7" id="how-should-we-get-this-built"><a href="/knowledge-hub/how-to-get-ai-for-your-project/how-should-we-get-this-built#how-should-we-get-this-built" class="govuk-link">4. How should we get this built?</a></h2>
              <p class="govuk-body">We have AI/tech expertise in our team.</p>
              <h2 class="govuk-heading-l govuk-!-margin-top-9" id="build-it-ourselves">Build it with your team</h2>
              <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How long?</h3>
              <p class="govuk-body">3 - 6+ months</p>
              <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Who to talk to</h3>
              <p class="govuk-body">Your tech team, data scientists, commercial team (for tools/infrastructure), ethics team.</p>
              <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What you'll need</h3>
              <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                  <li>Business case explaining why and how much (if over threshold)</li>
                  <li>Plan for avoiding bias in the AI</li>
                  <li>Plan for maintaining it long-term</li>
                  <li>Check sustainability and environmental impact</li>
                  <li>Compliance with Algorithmic Transparency Recording Standard (ATRS)</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="govuk-inset-text">
                  <p class="govuk-body"><span class="govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Consider:</span>  Could AI assistants like Copilot solve this more simply? You may still need to procure infrastructure or tools.</p>
